{"tid":1490355,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【重要】斬人風氣下必須急救知識","createTime":"2019-08-20T05:33:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T12:57:03.000Z","uid":259987,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"8095f3a7f17ce0188f017271e194d2e6292b5a6f","tid":1490355,"uid":259987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T05:33:53.000Z","msg":"八月二十日1點57分，景林去厚德連儂隧道有一男一女被人持菜刀斬。當時佢地只係痴緊sticker，就俾個人攞<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">菜刀</span></span>砍，其中一人<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">中頸</span></span>！<br />\n<br />\n所有手足都要同我學識點保護自己，點做刀傷既急救，對抗白色恐怖！唔好奉旨身邊一定會有FA啊！<br />\n<br />\n簡單幾個步驟：<br />\n1. 確認現場環境安全<br />\n2. 叫<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一個人</span></span> call 白車 e.g. 用手指住，叫「個位白色衫藍色長褲女士可唔可以叫白車！」一定要有人認頭先收聲。<br />\n3. 如果把刀仲插係度，唔撚好抆走佢，拍武俠片咩。俾傷者訓低休息，墊高傷口，要高過心臟。<br />\n4. 睇下究竟係咩傷，學下點處理：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UzRJqbg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUzRJqbg.png&h=5eb7684a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">1</span>直接按壓：<br />\n搵乾淨嘅布料，壓上傷口<br />\n(紗布 &gt; 毛巾 &gt; 衫 &gt; 紙巾)<br />\n如果傷口有異物或者斷骨凸出，唔好亂咁移動傷者既身體，要在傷口邊緣按壓。<br />\n大出血嘅話就唔好理條布乾唔乾淨，底褲都照冚上去啦。<br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">2</span>間接按壓：<br />\n綁傷口上方近心臟既位置，減慢血液流動。唔好綁太緊，用力可以放到一隻手指入去。太緊，15mins無血去四肢，會搞到手足要截肢。</span><br />\n <br />\n5. Mon 住心跳呼吸，問下佢問題，睇下清唔清醒<br />\n無心跳幾分鐘就救唔返，我地需要同佢做心外壓。冇呼吸嘅話，要同佢做人工呼吸。<br />\n <br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人，要守望相助！香港人，加油！</span></span></div>"},{"pid":"cf3c758793eeb3f3933a9c3439db335e4893412d","tid":1490355,"uid":259987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T05:34:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d9805172ff2667ef5c3d846d72ec5ba2c7df4e80","tid":1490355,"uid":181581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T05:37:29.000Z","msg":"公共圖書館有急救書可以睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"927e7b910ed01a6232c51a78bf4c7a3283c724c0","tid":1490355,"uid":259987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T05:39:18.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"943a5a702ff7b5148f07edbb8f0bf392bada8444","tid":1490355,"uid":259987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T05:46:27.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"93a923bd3a5fff9955789ac643e10a9ae4bdcbcf","tid":1490355,"uid":34489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T05:50:37.000Z","msg":"希望唔洗用到"},{"pid":"53e5822667dc3558cce318a57378f7144d181e1c","tid":1490355,"uid":72398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T05:51:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83fe8243662528316c96221f3b5866cd08796c84","tid":1490355,"uid":90004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T05:54:46.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />雖然唔想\b識，係而家依個香港大家要知"},{"pid":"91d5f15264eceecb0957c377156889c515330a66","tid":1490355,"uid":80277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T05:55:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k4XAgGn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk4XAgGn.png&h=4d1ea628&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xnOS3mn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxnOS3mn.png&h=4d22b9be&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oz9V072.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Foz9V072.png&h=8e01fd6a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DiEbzs3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.